# Internal / planning docs
# Policy: docs/ is a local planning/workspace tree (superpowers plans & specs) and
# stays ignored. Production-facing docs (README, GUIDE, SECURITY, OPERATIONS_RUNBOOK,
# PACKAGE_RELEASE_POLICY) live at the repo root so consumers can see them.
# Root planning artifacts (PRODUCTION_HARDENING_PLAN, HARDENING_HANDOFF, PROJECT_CONTEXT)
# are kept in-tree for maintainer/agent continuity but are excluded from npm tarballs
# by scripts/check-package-tarballs.mjs and the package "files" allowlist.
docs/
CLAUDE.md
AGENTS.md
GEMINI.md
